        "name": "Banish Falsehoods of Flesh",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "Your ability to manipulate supernatural energy allows you to deploy divine magic directly against a disguised enemy to reveal them as they truly are, or to cleanse an ally from an unwilling transformation. Attempt a Religion check to counteract a polymorph effect currently affecting a creature within 30 feet of you that you are aware of. The target is then temporarily immune to Banish Falsehoods of Flesh for 1 day.",
